../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/final-decider.md:22:Third, it retains the best ceiling compatible with this system. Chain 02 has the sharper Tao-sensitive novelty ceiling, but its positive branch depends on finding an explicit helical inequality that survives full reconstruction, which is a narrow and fragile event. Chain 03 is more likely to collapse into informative-but-noncoercive tensor language. Chain 01 is the only branch that can still end in a theorem-shaped compactness-rigidity package if one coherent starting package actually exists.
