+   - mild / maximal-lifespan critical-space evolutions,
+   - and any mixed bridge architecture if the repository actually supports one.
+2. What theorem-level contradiction endpoints or cash-out lines are locally
+   supported for those frameworks?
+   Examples: endpoint regularity exclusion, backward-uniqueness-style rigidity,
+   Liouville / ancient-solution exclusion, epsilon-regularity contradiction, or
